high_descs: Turn around and go to the garbage can, hang a left and go to the counter, turn to the right where the phone is.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn around and go to the dishwasher, hang a left and go to the end of the counter where the potato is.
Use the knife to cut the potato into slices.
Turn to the left, go towards the wall, hang a left, go past the counter, hang a left and turn to the garbage can on the right.
Put the knife in the garbage can.
Turn to the right, go past the counter, turn to the right, go to the wall, turn to the right, go to the counter on the right where the potato is.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn to the left and go to the counter, turn to the left and go to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave, turn it on to cook, remove the cooked potato from the microwave and close the door.
Turn around and go to the counter, hang a right and go to the garbage can that is on the left past the fridge.
Put the cooked potato in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and cooked potato in a garbage can.

high_descs: Turn around, walk around the counter, go to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the butter knife.
Turn around, walk to the counter, turn to the left, walk to the end of the counter on the left.
Slice the potato at the end of the counter.
Walk around the end of the counter, go to the wastebasket.
Put the butter knife in the wastebasket.
Turn around, walk back around to the other side of the counter.
Pick up the end slice of the potato.
Turn to the left, walk to the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave for a few seconds, take the potato out of the microwave.
Walk back to the wastebasket.
Put the potato in the wastebasket.
anns.task_desc: Throw away the end of the potato.

high_descs: Turn around, walk around the kitchen island to the fridge.  Then stand in front of the small counter just left of the fridge.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter to the left of the phone.
Turn around, walk around the island to the end furthest from the sink.  Face the right edge of the island with the sink on your left and the island between you and the fridge.
Slice half of the potato that is on the kitchen island just right of the egg.
Walk around the right edge of the island to face the trash can that is to the right of the fridge.
Put the knife into the trash can just behind the tomato.
Turn around and walk around the edge of the kitchen island (the edge with the chair), and face the right edge of the island with the sliced potato on it.
Pick up one slice of potato from off of the kitchen island, next to the egg.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, put the potato slice in the microwave and shut the door.  Microwave the potato slice for a few seconds, then take the slice out of the microwave, shutting the door.
Holding the potato slice, turn around and walk around the kitchen island to face the trash can that is to the right of the fridge.
Put the potato slice into the trash can, to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of potato into a trash can.
